{"tid":1994921,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣捉受傷嘅流浪貓去睇醫生？","createTime":"2020-04-29T22:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T02:04:19.000Z","uid":1863,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1cad343ccad3ff22fd5d3b5d5326f36039d9a1","tid":1994921,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T22:49:58.000Z","msg":"話說小弟我喺台灣讀書，搬咗過嚟三重都已經一段時間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搬咗過黎之後成日夜晚黑就會聽到樓下有隻貓喺度扑嘢，又或者一對三同其他貓喺度講數開片（真係中氣十足嗰隻feel），嘈到拆天。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但今晚落七仔印Notes嗰陣，見到嗰隻貓好似左前腳掌受咗傷，加上俾佢嘈咗成半年，都嘈咗啲感情出黎，就想話帶佢去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但捉浪浪去睇醫生最理想嘅步驟應該係點？用罐罐引佢出黎先？再擺佢落紙箱？再用綿羊仔車佢去獸醫度？我驚佢會反抗開我拖，所以應該會帶勞工手套再加著長袖衫先捉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲唔好怪我伸手牌，我只係驚我新手唔識嘢整到佢仲傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望各位巴絲可以俾下意見，話唔定第日我收養咗佢，各位連登仔女就係佢契爺契媽架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n循例講返句啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"78947bba42b002d115151e460738002950baa78d","tid":1994921,"uid":273803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T23:02:14.000Z","msg":"冇籠好難搞，你仲要新手，搵D 本地嘅貓義工幫手啦"},{"pid":"68e4f61b3e091da1cd4eecc5d026153688e0563b","tid":1994921,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T23:26:56.000Z","msg":"奴才認領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98ae1c1dd03cabc11878475aa6c982995747544","tid":1994921,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T04:29:35.000Z","msg":"Fb 台灣好多貓谷，搵義工幫手"},{"pid":"72241aa10e695e40895d9350e48fa13200764f2d","tid":1994921,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T22:31:48.000Z","msg":"搵台灣貓GRP幫手啦<br />\n佢地好多TNR經驗"},{"pid":"74907944586659f751310e442b44e76fcbbf5c24","tid":1994921,"uid":119396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T04:21:51.000Z","msg":"通常唔會用手捉，借個識自動落閘嘅籠放嘢食入去等佢食就得"},{"pid":"a6a0fea1f8c10e7b137e2876cfbfe731d39010b7","tid":1994921,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T20:47:31.000Z","msg":"冇貓籠唔會捉到。<br />\n買咗籠之後用肉泥引誘。"},{"pid":"e26e24af949a2f31a39e76d32c68f0c27ac3779a","tid":1994921,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:04:19.000Z","msg":"租一個貓籠，把貓困住. <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=how+to+trap+a+stray+cat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fresults%3Fsearch_query%3Dhow%2Bto%2Btrap%2Ba%2Bstray%2Bcat&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=7ddbf7fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=how+to+trap+a+stray+cat</a><br />\n<br />\n嘗試這些組織，看看他們是否可以藉給您一個貓籠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hotac.org.tw/default.asp?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hotac.org.tw%2Fdefault.asp%3F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=6845dc02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hotac.org.tw/default.asp?</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%89%E9%87%8D%E7%B8%BD%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9B%E5%BF%83%E8%B2%93%E5%92%AA%E5%B1%8B%E9%80%81%E9%A4%8A%E6%9C%83-%E7%A4%BE%E5%9C%98%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%B5%81%E6%B5%AA%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83-167849783290710/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25B2%2593%25E5%2592%25AA%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%25A4%258A%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%259C%2598%2